ot%3Bgets%20to%20know%26quot%3B%20users'%20preferences%2C%20remembers%20context%2C%20and%20is%20personalized.%20It's%20also%20a%20companion%20app%20for%20Meta's%20AI-powered%20Ray-Ban%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20competitors%3A%20The%20new%20app%20has%20a%20social%20feed%20where%20users%20can%20share%20what%20they%20are%20prompting%20Meta's%20AI%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20app's%20arrival%2C%20Meta%20onboarded%20creators%20so%20the%20feed%20wasn't%20a%20content%20desert%20and%20also%20sought%20their%20feedback.%20The%20day%20of%20its%20launch%2C%20Meta%20AI's%20%26quot%3BDiscover%26quot%3B%20feed%20was%20already%20filled%20with%20AI%20prompts%20from%20Meta%20employees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20content%20creators%20like%20travel%20bloggers%2C%20meme%20makers%2C%20tech%20enthusiasts%2C%20and%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20creator%20partnership%20teams%20reached%20out%20to%20influencers%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20to%20onboard%20them%20to%20the%20new%20app%2C%20multiple%20creators%20and%20talent%20managers%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20These%20content%20creators%20got%20early%20access%20to%20Meta%20AI%20last%20week%2C%20but%20said%20they%20were%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-paying-creators-exclusive-content-deals-reels-contract-details-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaid%20by%20Meta%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20use%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7b72156-b64e-4908-975c-bbe1b4b30e0e%5C%22%3EHow%20creators%20are%20using%20Meta%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDay%20one%20of%20Meta%20AI's%20feed%20included%20a%20mix%20of%20prompts%20shared%20by%20creators.%20Some%20shared%20images%20the%20AI%20generated%2C%20such%20as%20versions%20of%20themselves%20with%20different%20colored%20eyes.%20Others%20shared%20text%20prompts%20like%20%26quot%3B100%20men%20vs%201%20gorilla%2C%20who%20will%20win%3F%26quot%3B%20posted%20by%20the%20meme%20page%20Hoodville%20(which%20has%209%20million%20Instagram%20followers).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20choose%20what%20prompts%20they%20share%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20going%20to%20be%20every%20thought%20that%20I%20have%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20really%20curated%2C%26quot%3B%20meme%20creator%20Vanessa%20Vice%20said.%20One%20of%20her%20first%20public%20prompts%20was%20asking%20Meta%20AI%20to%20%26quot%3Bimagine%20the%20average%20John%20Mayer%20fan%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20then%20spit%20out%20images%20of%20John%20Mayer%20wearing%20John%20Mayer%20merch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20app's%20Discover%20feed%20is%20like%20a%20version%20of%20the%20OG%20Facebook%20Feed%20but%20only%20focused%20on%20AI%20use%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mike%20Proulx%2C%20a%20VP%20at%20Forrester%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20AI's%20social%20features%20are%20limited%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20users%20can%20like%20posts%2C%20reply%20to%20other%20people's%20AI%20prompts%2C%20and%20share%20posts%20to%20other%20apps%20like%20Instagram%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20or%20Threads%2C%20Meta%20AI%20isn't%20a%20full-fledged%20social%20media%20platform%20yet.%20For%20instance%2C%20there%20is%20currently%20no%20way%20to%20follow%20any%20profiles%20on%20the%20app%2C%20although%20some%20creators%20have%20their%20Instagram%20pages%20linked%20to%20their%20Meta%20AI%20profiles.%20There%20also%20isn't%20a%20way%20to%20search%20for%20creators%20or%20public%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20necessarily%20about%20building%20a%20following%20on%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andrew%20Wille%2C%20a%20photographer%20who%20got%20early%20access%20to%20Meta%20AI.%20Instead%2C%20Wille%20said%20he's%20using%20the%20public%20feed%20to%20%26quot%3Blearn%20how%20to%20best%20prompt%20Meta%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20educational%20component%20is%20a%20core%20part%20of%20the%20Meta%20AI%20app%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20post%20any%20o