0nautical%20miles%3B%20it's%20typically%20guided%20by%20radar%20against%20air%20targets.%20In%20its%20fully%20automatic%20firing%20mode%2C%20it%20can%20fire%20up%20to%2020%20rounds%20a%20minute%20with%20an%20autoloader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArleigh%20Burke-class%20destroyers%20carry%20600%20rounds%20of%20conventional%20ammunition%2C%20while%20Ticonderoga-class%20cruisers%2C%C2%A0which%20have%20two%20Mark%2045s%2C%C2%A0can%20hold%201%2C200%20shells.%20This%20is%20a%20far%20greater%20magazine%20depth%20than%20the%20air-defense%20missile%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20class%20of%20destroyers%20is%20equipped%20with%20as%20many%20as%2096%20vertical%20launching%20system%20cells%2C%20while%20the%20cruisers%20are%20equipped%20with%20around%20120%20VLS%20cells.%20Not%20all%20these%20launch%20tubes%20carry%20the%20Navy's%20Standard%20Missile%20interceptors%2C%20like%20the%20SM-2%2C%20SM-3%2C%20or%20SM-6.%20They%20are%20also%20equipped%20with%20land-attack%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225817%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20destroyer%20USS%20Benfold%20fires%20its%20MK45%20five-inch%20gun%20during%20a%20live-fire%20drill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6810f4fca466d2b74ab474a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223910%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20five-inch%20deck%20gun%20can%20fire%20up%20to%2020%20rounds%20of%20conventional%20ammunition%20a%20minute.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%202nd%20Class%20Deanna%20C.%20Gonzales%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthi-missile-close-us-warship-close-in-weapon-system-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurface-to-air%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20appear%20to%20be%20the%20main%20air-defense%20tool%20that%20US%20and%20European%20warships%20have%20used%20to%20eliminate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-learning-battles-houthi-anti-ship-ballistic-missiles-commanders-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouthi%20drones%20and%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20deck%20gun%20engagements%20suggest%20the%20weapon%20could%20be%20useful%20in%20future%20maritime%20conflicts%20where%20drones%20are%20prominent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBradley%20Martin%2C%20a%20retired%20Navy%20surface%20warfare%20captain%2C%20said%20that%20while%20the%20naval%20deck%20gun%20was%20always%20intended%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20layered%20defense%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-red-sea-lost-another-fighter-jet-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Red%20Sea%20conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20this%20weapon%20is%20ideal%20for%20destroying%20small%20attack%20drones%20that%20fly%20slower%20than%20a%20cruise%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaritime%20drones%20can%20be%20launched%20in%20large%20numbers%20and%20are%20relatively%20cheap%20compared%20to%20other%20munitions.%20%26quot%3BA%20gun%20provides%20an%20inexpensive%20counter%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Martin%2C%20now%20a%20senior%20policy%20researcher%20at%20RAND.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20learning%20is%20that%20having%20short-range%20kinetic%20capability%2C%20like%20a%20gun%20offers%2C%20is%20very%20valuable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20longer-range%20kinetic%20capability%2C%20like%20the%20SM-2%2C%20can%20strike%20enemy%20aircraft%20or%20anti-ship%20missiles%20some%2090%20nautical%20miles%20away.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Fcost-and-value-air-and-missile-defense-intercepts%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThese%2520data%2520points%2520are%2520frequently%2Cto%2520intercept%2520%25242%252C000%2520Houthi%2520drones.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20a%20%242%20million%20price%20tag%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20a%20significantly%20more%20expensive%20option%20than%20a%20Mk-45%20round%20for%20taking%20out%20a%20cheap%20drone%20worth%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221083%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20French%20helicopter%20shot%20down%20a%20Houthi%20attack%20drone%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%20March.%20Houthi%20rebels%20have%20since%20used%20their%20UAVs%20to%20threaten%20ships%20far%20beyond%20the%20Red%20Sea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647c7a314fb5b23cc5e0563%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22733%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Houthis%20have%20used%20explosive-packed%20drones%20to%20threaten%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20the%20adjacent%20Gulf%20of%20Aden.%3Cp%3EFrench%20Army%2FHandout%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20said%20that%20deck%20guns%20are%20a%20good%20way%20to%20get%20ordnance%20out%20quickly%20and%20can%20be%20used%20in%20various%20ways.%20A%20warship%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20may%20track%20a%20target%20via%20radar%20or%20a%20camera%20and%20fire%20precisely%20at%20it%3B%20alternatively%2C%20air%20burst%20rounds%20can%20release%20lots%20of%20shrapnel%20into%20the%20air%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20a%20drone%20to%20pass%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20warships%20are%20armed%20with%20other%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsailors-us-navy-gravely-destroyer-have-seconds-respond-houthi-missiles-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefend%20themselves%20at%20closer%20ranges%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well.%20These%20include%20the%20Phalanx%20Close-In%20Weapon%20System%20(CIWS)%20and%20Evolved%20Sea%20Sparrow%20Missiles.%20A%20US%20warship%20had%20a%20close%20call%20with%20an%20incoming%20missile%20early%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20fight%20that%20required%20CIWS%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArcher%20Macy%2C%20a%20retired%20Navy%20admiral%2C%20said%20that%20it's%20ultimately%20the%20job%20of%20the%20vessel's%20combat%20system%20and%20the%20operators%20to%20best%20align%20each%20weapon%20with%20the%20incoming%20threat.%20He%20noted%20that%20while%20a%