ption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon's%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20has%20advice%20for%20companies%20that%20want%20to%20cut%20management%20layers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAndy%20Jassy%20said%20companies%20should%20have%20a%20solid%20feedback%20loop%20in%20place%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20biggest%20problems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20said%20companies%20need%20to%20keep%20working%20on%20resolving%20the%20issue%20if%20they%20want%20to%20see%20change.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandy-jassy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndy%20Jassy%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20company%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20%26quot%3Boperate%20like%20the%20world's%20largest%20startup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20flatten%20our%20organizations%2C%20to%20move%20faster%20and%20to%20drive%20more%20ownership%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Amazon%20CEO%20said%20during%20a%20speaking%20event%20at%20the%20Harvard%20Business%20Review%20Leadership%20Summit%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-rto-issues-space-security-productivity-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive-day%20return%20to%20office%20mandate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amazon%20has%20undertaken%20a%20plan%20to%20increase%20the%20ratio%20of%20individual%20contributors%20to%20managers%20by%20at%20least%2015%25%20across%20the%20company.%20Jassy%20said%20it%20will%20have%20beaten%20that%20goal%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20said%20the%20company%20hasn't%20perfected%20its%20mission%20yet%2C%20but%20companies%20wanting%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20path%20of%20reducing%20bureaucracy%20should%20follow%20these%20three%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d23c1618-bd2d-4ad2-995e-c06bd4e4